'''阿根廷蛇頸龜'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Hydromedusa tectifera''）<ref name="zipcode">[http://www.zipcodezoo.com/animals/h/hydromedusa_tectifera.asp Zipcodezoo.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.zipcodezoo.com/animals/h/hydromedusa_tectifera.asp |date=20070930031150 }} URL accessed March 24, 2007.</ref> 亦稱'''刻紋漁龜'''，是[[漁龜屬|漁龜屬]]下的一種蛇頸龜，常被當作寵物龜來飼養。這種龜可能與[[枯葉龜|枯葉龜]]有更密切的親緣關係，<ref name="tortoise"/> 發現於[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]、[[烏拉圭|烏拉圭]]、[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]和[[巴西|巴西]]南部。<ref>[http://www.flmnh.ufl.edu/natsci/herpetology/turtcroclist/chklst14.htm Hydromedusa] {{Wayback|url=http://www.flmnh.ufl.edu/natsci/herpetology/turtcroclist/chklst14.htm |date=20080124215739 }} URL accessed March 28, 2007.</ref> 關於這種龜的研究並不多。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20060602053051/http://calvados.c3sl.ufpr.br/ojs2/index.php/veterinary/article/viewPDFInterstitial/3943/3183 ANIMAL HOUSE SYSTEM FOR FRESHWATER TURTLE] URL accessed March 29, 2007.</ref>

==解剖學與形態學==
